Title: Legacy checks: fix usage of discovery rulesets
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1605013343
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0b1

For certain legacy checks, some discovery rulesets were not applied
correctly (e.g. the discovery ruleset "Filesystem grouping patterns"
for the <tt>df</tt>-check). This has been fixed.
